      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even about being tired. it's just that the person everyone thinks i am... they don't exist. it's all just a script. if i stop performing, there's literally nothing left. it feels like i'm just waiting for the credits to roll because the movie is already over.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
